2. **Template Consistency**: Every service/location page uses the exact H1-H2-CTA schema. Only swap `[Service]`, `[Price]`, `[Location]`, and `[Keywords]`
3. **WhatsApp Pre-fill Logic**: 
   - Emergency pages: `?text=EMERGENCY%20[Location]%20[Issue]`
   - Service pages: `?text=QUOTE%20[ServiceName]%20[Suburb]%20[Issue]`
